des:
Zebronics Home products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off smart plugs. 

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your connect appliances - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Zebronics smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “ZEB Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Zebronics smart account in our “ZEB Home" app;
(3). You need to have some Zebronics smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “ZEB Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in “Zebronics Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search “Zebronics Home” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of “Zebronics Home", and you'll be navigated to ZEB Home login page;
(9). Input your ZEB Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"

Currently this skill supports products:
smart switch,
smart socket, 
smart bulb….
